SUMMARY:Easter Egg Hunt
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Easter Egg Decorating with Reverend Anya on Saturday\, April 4\, 2026 from 10:00 AM to 12:00 PM. All Ages welcome in Fletcher Hall. Eggs and Supplies will be provided. Wear clothing that can get messy! \nThe EGG HUNT on April 5\, 2026 is one of our favorite events to gather children and youth (yes\, even the older kids come out for this event)\, for an afternoon of searching the UUCM grounds for BRIGHTLY COLORED goodies. \nIf you would like to help defray the expenses of this EGG-TASTICALLY FUN EVENT we do have some much-needed HUNT items on an Amazon Wish List. Click the LINK for the Wish List: https://a.co/0eSioS2t \nPlease let us know how many children will participate in these events so that we have enough supplies. Thank you! \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
