SUMMARY:Flower Crown Making Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Transform fresh\, seasonal flowers into a wearable masterpiece in this hands-on creative session. You’ll learn to construct a flower crown using flower wires for a custom fit and flower tapes for a seamless\, secure finish. Perfect for festivals or gifts\, this workshop leaves you with a beautiful handcrafted crown and the skills to create more at home. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
